734	3	What is the nerve supply of the biceps brachii muscle?	Radial nerve	Ulnar nerve	Musculocutaneous nerve	Median nerve	C	This is Biceps brachii muscle\n• It is innervated by the musculocutaneous nerve (C5-C6)\nFunctions of biceps brachii:\n• Flexion of elbow\n• Supination of forearm\n• Weak shoulder flexion	99	2026-07-13 03:07:34.881424	\N
